App Info The purpose of the app Addis Ababa is the capital of Ethiopia and the largest city in East Africa. It is a bustling metropolis with a rich history and culture. There are many things to see and do in Addis Ababa, from visiting historical sites to shopping in the markets.
A smart tourism app for Addis Ababa would be a great way to help visitors find their way around the city and discover all that it has to offer. The app could include features such as a map of the city, information on attractions and events, and a way to book tours and activities.
The app could also be used to provide information on the city\'s history and culture. This would be a valuable resource for visitors who want to learn more about Addis Ababa.
Overall, a smart tourism app for Addis Ababa would be a great way to help visitors make the most of their trip to the city. It would provide them with information and resources that would make their visit more enjoyable and memorable.
Current features • Add/capture businesses, institutions, companies and tourist attraction locations • Search and locate businesses, institutions, companies and tourist attraction locations
Upcoming features • A map of the city with points of interest marked. • Detailed Information on attractions and events • A way to book tours, hotels and activities • Information on the city’s history and culture • A way to communicate with other visitors • A way to get help in case of an emergency • Information on water, electricity and traffic of different areas in Addis
